<DOCID> 49701 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
April 27, 1989, Thursday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part 3; Page 1; Column 2; Sports Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
