<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEWSWIRE: NAMES IN THE NEWS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
David Atchison, golf coach at UC Santa Barbara since 1982, was named to the 
same position at UCLA, replacing Eddie Merrins, who retired. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Column 
</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
UNIVERSITY OF CALIFORNIA AT LOS ANGELES; GOLF; COACHES 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
